[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "……というわけで、「亜空の道」というものが\nこの世界にはあるそうだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "へえ～、なんだかすごく便利そうなものですね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "でもそれって、わたしたちが使ってる「飴」とは\n違うものなのかな？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "ぜんぜん違うじゃない。\n「飴」はアトリエを介した移動しかできないし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "使える状況も整えないといけないですしね。\nいざという時に「飴」は使いづらいです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "そうだな。「亜空の道」を自在に創れたら\n良かったんだけどな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "今はその技術もほとんど残っていないんだよね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "はい。今あるのは、アルマの大樹の根に繋がる\n「亜空の道」だけだそうです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "うーん、でも「飴」があるだけで相当便利ですし、\n別に困ってはないですよね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "そうそう。\nあたしは「飴」で十分だと思うけど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "まあな。より便利なものを追求しようとするのは\n技術屋の悪い癖か……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "でも、もしどこでも好きな場所を\n直接繋げることができたら……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "危険な場所にいる仲間を、遠くからでも\nすぐ助けに行けるのにね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "うん……それができたら、わたしもおねーちゃんの\nピンチにすぐ駆け付けられるのに",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "でも、そんな都合のいい道があったら、\n悪いことに使う人も出てきそうじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "それもそうか……過ぎた技術には、\n常にその問題が付きまとうな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "……でも、夢はあるよね。わたし、いつか\nみんなの力で新しい道を創ってみたいかも",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "エスカ",
		"romanized_name": "Escha",
		"model_path_hash": "4942920317009730088",
		"text": "そうですね！　わたしたちの中で悪いことに使う人\nなんていないでしょうし！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8567200502263774699",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（なになに？　離れた所を繋ぐ道？\n　……それ、イタズラし放題じゃん！）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（あたしの天才的ヒラメキが、\n　また１つ増えちゃったってわけ！）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]